title: Rula Bula
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Irish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Bar near ASU campus, open daily til late. Food menu includes a vegetarian shepard's pie and a plowman's veggie sandwich, both of which can be request to omit cheese. There's also a few other appetizers that are veggie suitable. Sometimes the kitchen will substitute veggie patty on any of the burgers.
